text: Harjan Visscher (born 26 February 1997) is a Dutch korfball player. He is a member of LDODK (since May 2022) and the Netherlands national korfball team. With the national team he won the gold medal at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. Visscher has a relationship with korfball player Marieke Klaver. ==Achievements== ===Club=== *Korfbal League champion, 1x (2022) * champion, 1x (2019) * champion, 1x (2019) ===National team=== *World Games champion, 2x (2017, 2022) *World champion, 1x (2019) *European champion, 1x (2021) ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch korfball players
